>>>>>> AI Appointment Scheduler <<<<<<
Schedule Google Calendar appointments effortlessly using natural language.

Features
1. Natural Language Input: Describe appointments (e.g., "Meeting with Mr.xyz tomorrow at 3 PM").
2. AI-Powered: Uses Gemini AI for detail extraction.
3. Google Calendar Integration: Creates events directly.
4. Smart Time Handling: Adjusts dates/times as needed.
Setup
1. Code: Save the provided Python code as project.py.
2. Google Credentials (credentials.json):
   i)   Get this file from Google Cloud Console.
   ii)  Enable the Google Calendar API.
   iii) Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID for "Desktop app".
   iv)  Place credentials.json in the same directory as project.py.
3. Gemini API Key:
  i)    Get your API key from Google AI Studio.
  ii)   Create a file named .env in the same directory as project.py.
  iii)  Add Gemini-API="YOUR_API_KEY_HERE" to .env.
4. Install Dependencies: pip install streamlit google-api-python-client google-auth-oauthlib google-auth-httplib2 python-dotenv langchain-google-genai langgraph
